{
  "stem": "5470.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It even was so, at one stage-- and now you can see actually how that worked-- Gemmeker was practically every day, save for a moment in the camp, that he walked around and so on.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he came on the bicycle one day in the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And what happened actually, I don't know, but he hit Schlesinger accidentally, and he broke his leg.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now usually that would have been the consequence that he was off, outside, gone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "No control whatsoever anymore and reappoint a different one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nothing of the kind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He had the little unit in the camp for his own, a two bedroom-- a one bedroom unit.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Living area, bedroom, kitchen, toilet, little, tiny one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Just about that space, divided into different sections.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he had-- [COUGHS] His own family life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They had big, big barracks for the others.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But these old ones, they had just a normal family life, although it was small.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And well, he went into the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "His leg was put in plaster, and he had to lie down for about four to six weeks, something like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And what happened, Gemmeker came every day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But before he went every day to his office outside the camp, now Gemmeker came every day inside the camp in his own unit.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that's where they discussed what, what had to happen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he just did his whole controlling business from his sick bed at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "A strange situation.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He left everything up to Schlesinger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He wasn't popular, but he wasn't unpopular either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But say for a part of the community, they didn't like him at all, especially for the Dutch people, of course.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
